    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1898-02-19T14:50:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1898-02-19T14:50:00-05:00" n="1019"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1019">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">President</gloss> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Woodford</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Executive Mansion</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-02-19T14:50:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 19, 1898</hi>—2.50 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Convey in appropriate manner my sincere appreciation of Her Majesty’s message of
                    condolence and sympathy as conveyed in your telegram just received.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">William McKinley.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
